---
title: Lemony Chickpea & Arugula Grain Salad with Cucumber, Cheddar & Sunflower Seeds
description: For a delicious, wholesome salad, you’ll start by sizzling chickpeas and scallion whites, then toss them with tender grains, cheddar cheese, arugula, cucumber, and sunflower seeds. Drizzle with a simple lemony olive oil dressing and finish with scallion greens for a nourishing meal that’s ready in less than 15 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65f0be87f15f35246a8cb573-9bc465dc.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65f0be87f15f35246a8cb573.pdf
